---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="py-section-padding px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto relative">
    <img
      alt="Pulsi Benefits"
      class="absolute -right-12 -top-24 w-40 h-40 hidden lg:block opacity-80"
      src={`${base}images/beneficios.png`}
    />
    <h2 class="text-center font-headline-xl text-headline-xl mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Más visibilidad. <br class="hidden md:block" /> Decisiones oportunas. <br
        class="hidden md:block"
      /> Equipos más equilibrados.
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-gutter">
      <div
        class="p-10 rounded-3xl bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/30 flex flex-col items-center text-center bento-card"
      >
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-primary-container/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl">radar</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg mb-4">Detecta</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body-md">
          Identifica señales tempranas antes de que se conviertan en problemas.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="p-10 rounded-3xl bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/30 flex flex-col items-center text-center bento-card"
      >
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-secondary-container/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-4xl">search</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg mb-4">Comprende</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body-md">
          Visualiza tendencias, causas probables y factores recurrentes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="p-10 rounded-3xl bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/30 flex flex-col items-center text-center bento-card"
      >
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-tertiary-container/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary text-4xl">task_alt</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg mb-4">Actúa</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body-md">
          Recibe recomendaciones concretas para apoyar mejores decisiones.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
